“de_churchtown”


This map was custom made for a tournament in Christchurch, New Zealand.

This is a fast paced Defuse/ Bomb map.
The terrorist must destroy the Ammo Cache or the Weapon Crates to win.

- 64 Spawns
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Overview radar map
- 3d skybox
- Buy Zones
- Nav File for bots
- Soundscapes
- Pakrated into one .bsp file
- Original content created by Valve


Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt – Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
